narratives.question_text: How would you summarize ECON 110 05 for a fellow student? Would you recommend ECON 110 05 to another student? Why or why not?
comments: I would recommend this for anyone who really means to dedicate the time and attention necessary to do it right.
If you are writing a year long senior essay, now is the crunch time. Enjoy. I got a lot out of the experience, but it's tough going and you need to be sure to motivate yourself.
